  "instructions": [
    "Prepare the chicken by trimming any excess fat, slicing it into thin pieces, and season with salt and pepper.",
    "Heat sesame oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat. Add scallions, ginger, lemon leaves, Thai basil, fish sauce, and soy sauce. Stir well to combine.",
    "Add chicken to the pan and stir-fry for 5-7 minutes until cooked through, turning occasionally.",
    "Serve hot with steamed jasmine rice."
